# DECISIONS.md

> Lightweight architecture decision records. Log non-trivial choices and their reasoning.
> **Update**: per decision. Append, don't rewrite.

A decision is worth logging if a future-you reading this would say _"interesting, I might have done it differently"_ or _"I'm glad I know why this happened"_.

Skip trivia (variable names, formatting, etc.).

---

## Template

```
## YYYY-MM-DD: <one-line decision>

**Context**: <why this decision was needed>

**Choice**: <what we decided>

**Alternatives considered**:
- <option A> — rejected because <reason>
- <option B> — rejected because <reason>

**Reversibility**: <easy / moderate / hard to undo later>

**Open follow-ups** (optional): <things we deferred>
```

